{"sectionId":660,"sectionIdLiteral":"660","humanId":"lesson-246","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"To love my Father is to love His Son.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 246"},"annotation":"W-246","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-246\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"660#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"660#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Let me not think that I can find the way to God, if I have hatred in my heart.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"660#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Let me not try to hurt God‚Äôs Son, and think that I can know his Father or my Self.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"660#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Let me not fail to recognize myself, and still believe that my awareness can contain my Father, or my mind conceive of all the love my Father has for me, and all the love which I return to Him.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"660#2\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"660#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>I will accept the way You choose for me to come to You, my Father.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"660#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>For in that will I succeed, because it is Your Will.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"660#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And I would recognize that what You will is what I will as well, and only that.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"660#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>And so I choose to love Your Son.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"660#2:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>Amen.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Let me not think that I can find the way to God, if I have hatred in my heart. Let me not try to hurt God‚Äôs Son, and think that I can know his Father or my Self. Let me not fail to recognize myself,","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 246: To love my Father is to love His Son | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß